platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 有趣的貓咪跑酷探險之旅！

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Outfit7’s beloved Talking Tom series has another winner. Everything in this endless runner pops—its adorably detailed visuals, its cool-as-ice tunes, the constant surprises in the action-packed environments. Getting to play as Tom’s fuzzy friends just cranks up the fun even higher.
